										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="rss-image"><p><img src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Top-Speed-Comparison-datastream.jpg" alt="What's Faster, Nature or Machine?"/></p>
<p><center><span class="bg-showmore-enable-customized-display"><input type='hidden' bg_collapse_expand_pro='61c98b0ad6d875074791673' value=61c98b0ad6d875074791673><input type='hidden' id='bg-show-more-text-61c98b0ad6d875074791673' value='▼ Use This Visualization'><input type='hidden' id='bg-show-less-text-61c98b0ad6d875074791673' value='Show Less'><input type='hidden' id='bg-icon-bg-color-61c98b0ad6d875074791673' value=''><div id='bg-showmore-pro-hidden-61c98b0ad6d875074791673' class='bg-showmore-closed ' ></p>
