</table>
<!-- #tablepress-2024 from cache -->
<p style="margin-top:0px; font-size:15px;"><em>Source: MSCI (2020)</em></p>
<p>This leadership may bring further interest to the UK equity market, especially as awareness around social issues continues to rise. </p>
<h2>#4: UK Equities Can be a Compelling Source of Income</h2>
<p>Over a 10-year time frame, UK dividends rates have exceeded those of other global markets. </p>

<table id="tablepress-2025" class="tablepress tablepress-id-2025">
<thead>
<tr class="row-1 odd">
	<th class="column-1">Country/Region</th><th class="column-2">Dividend Yield (as of Sept. 30, 2021)</th><th class="column-3">Dividend Yield (10-year median) </th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class="row-hover">
